Text.SourceString: Why hello there, if it isn't a human wandering into my domain... Now, who might you be?
Text.LocalizedString: Why hello there, if it isn't a human wandering into my domain... Now, who might you be?

Text.SourceString: Welcome to my humble shop. I'm not entirely sure you've got what it takes to handle my collection, but let's see, shall we?
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome to my humble shop. I'm not entirely sure you've got what it takes to handle my collection, but let's see, shall we?

Text.SourceString: Oh, the buffaloes? Marvelous milk producers, yes, they are.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, the buffaloes? Marvelous milk producers, yes, they are.

Text.SourceString: I tell you, milking a buffalo is an experience. It's like they know they're in charge, and you're just the hired help.// Consider this a friendly, free warning.
Text.LocalizedString: I tell you, milking a buffalo is an experience. It's like they know they're in charge, and you're just the hired help.// Consider this a friendly, free warning.

Text.SourceString: My ostriches lay the most amazing quality eggs – absolute stars, unlike anything you've ever seen before.//They're not your average breakfast eggs.
Text.LocalizedString: My ostriches lay the most amazing quality eggs – absolute stars, unlike anything you've ever seen before.//They're not your average breakfast eggs.

Text.SourceString: Oh sure, the desert is just sand and sun, and I'm just a talking panther selling oversized birds and gentle giants.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh sure, the desert is just sand and sun, and I'm just a talking panther selling oversized birds and gentle giants.

Text.SourceString: A day in the desert? Hot, sandy, and full of surprises – kind of like my last blind date, minus the ostriches.
Text.LocalizedString: A day in the desert? Hot, sandy, and full of surprises – kind of like my last blind date, minus the ostriches.

Text.SourceString: Well, look who's braved the desert sands to visit my humble abode! Welcome!
Text.LocalizedString: Well, look who's braved the desert sands to visit my humble abode! Welcome!

Text.SourceString: Hello there! Have you come to adopt one of my shining stars?
Text.LocalizedString: Hello there! Have you come to adopt one of my shining stars?

Text.SourceString: Ah, it's you again! Come in, my human friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, it's you again! Come in, my human friend.

Text.SourceString: Ah, a visitor! Come in. Have you had a chance to check out my stars?
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, a visitor! Come in. Have you had a chance to check out my stars?

Text.SourceString: Out here in the desert, survival's a bit like a dance – you have to stay light on your feet and always be ready to follow nature's lead.//My stars, the animals, they're masters at it.
Text.LocalizedString: Out here in the desert, survival's a bit like a dance – you have to stay light on your feet and always be ready to follow nature's lead.//My stars, the animals, they're masters at it.

Text.SourceString: If you want to survive the desert, watch my stars closely. The way a buffalo finds water, or an ostrich stays cool, there's wisdom there.
Text.LocalizedString: If you want to survive the desert, watch my stars closely. The way a buffalo finds water, or an ostrich stays cool, there's wisdom there.

Text.SourceString: The desert's a tough teacher, but pay attention, and it'll show you its secrets.
Text.LocalizedString: The desert's a tough teacher, but pay attention, and it'll show you its secrets.

Text.SourceString: Each buffalo, each ostrich has its own personality. It's all about understanding and respect. Remember that, human.
Text.LocalizedString: Each buffalo, each ostrich has its own personality. It's all about understanding and respect. Remember that, human.

Text.SourceString: The desert's more than just sand and sun; it's a living, breathing world.//But the endless sands and the warm sun are definitely my favorite parts.
Text.LocalizedString: The desert's more than just sand and sun; it's a living, breathing world.//But the endless sands and the warm sun are definitely my favorite parts.

Text.SourceString: Always keep your eyes open for an oasis, but don't be fooled by mirages.
Text.LocalizedString: Always keep your eyes open for an oasis, but don't be fooled by mirages.

Text.SourceString: Never underestimate the importance of a good shade. In the desert, a little shadow can be your best companion, second only to a reliable water source.
Text.LocalizedString: Never underestimate the importance of a good shade. In the desert, a little shadow can be your best companion, second only to a reliable water source.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the cavern? You've probably heard the tales – whispers of it being haunted.//It's wise to steer clear of that place. Even my bravest stars won't venture near it.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the cavern? You've probably heard the tales – whispers of it being haunted.//It's wise to steer clear of that place. Even my bravest stars won't venture near it.

Text.SourceString: There's a chill around that cavern, a kind that seeps into your bones.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a chill around that cavern, a kind that seeps into your bones.

Text.SourceString: Legend has it that the cavern holds more than just shadows. They talk of spirits lingering in its depths.
Text.LocalizedString: Legend has it that the cavern holds more than just shadows. They talk of spirits lingering in its depths.

Text.SourceString: Finding food out here is a daily adventure.//Sometimes, the desert is generous, offering up bountiful harvests; other times, it teaches you the art of patience.
Text.LocalizedString: Finding food out here is a daily adventure.//Sometimes, the desert is generous, offering up bountiful harvests; other times, it teaches you the art of patience.

Text.SourceString: We may share conversations, but our lives are worlds apart.//It's fascinating, really. You walk on two legs, talk in your human ways, while I...well, I'm <Italic>this</>.
Text.LocalizedString: We may share conversations, but our lives are worlds apart.//It's fascinating, really. You walk on two legs, talk in your human ways, while I...well, I'm <Italic>this</>.

Text.SourceString: It's always amusing to see your kind trying to navigate the sands. It's like watching a fish climb a tree – admirable, but out of place.
Text.LocalizedString: It's always amusing to see your kind trying to navigate the sands. It's like watching a fish climb a tree – admirable, but out of place.

Text.SourceString: Every time a human visits, it's a source of entertainment. You walk so differently, so upright and careful, like the sand is a puzzle to be solved.
Text.LocalizedString: Every time a human visits, it's a source of entertainment. You walk so differently, so upright and careful, like the sand is a puzzle to be solved.

Text.SourceString: It's not every day I get to observe a human in the wild.
Text.LocalizedString: It's not every day I get to observe a human in the wild.

Text.SourceString: Speak, my friend, is that why you humans are slow? Relying on just two legs instead of four? It's a curious choice.
Text.LocalizedString: Speak, my friend, is that why you humans are slow? Relying on just two legs instead of four? It's a curious choice.

Text.SourceString: I got these golden bangles from a traveling merchant.//A human, living in a house on wheels. Ken, I think his name was, or something like that.
Text.LocalizedString: I got these golden bangles from a traveling merchant.//A human, living in a house on wheels. Ken, I think his name was, or something like that.

Text.SourceString: I remember our encounter well. His rolling house was like nothing I'd ever seen.
Text.LocalizedString: I remember our encounter well. His rolling house was like nothing I'd ever seen.

Text.SourceString: This necklace is a part of who I am. It's not for sale, no matter the offer.
Text.LocalizedString: This necklace is a part of who I am. It's not for sale, no matter the offer.

Text.SourceString: I cherish this necklace; it's as dear to me as the desert sky. Selling it would be like parting with a piece of my soul.
Text.LocalizedString: I cherish this necklace; it's as dear to me as the desert sky. Selling it would be like parting with a piece of my soul.

Text.SourceString: I've left the life of hunting behind. Now, my focus is on caring for my stars.
Text.LocalizedString: I've left the life of hunting behind. Now, my focus is on caring for my stars.

Text.SourceString: Hunting is no longer my way.  These days, I find more joy in nurturing life than chasing it.
Text.LocalizedString: Hunting is no longer my way.  These days, I find more joy in nurturing life than chasing it.

Text.SourceString: There was a time when hunting was my nature, but not anymore. Now, I am a guardian, a keeper of the desert's wonders.
Text.LocalizedString: There was a time when hunting was my nature, but not anymore. Now, I am a guardian, a keeper of the desert's wonders.

Text.SourceString: The idea of venturing beyond the desert has never appealed to me. Everything I need is right here amidst these dunes.
Text.LocalizedString: The idea of venturing beyond the desert has never appealed to me. Everything I need is right here amidst these dunes.

Text.SourceString: This desert, with its harsh beauty and rugged charm, is home. Why seek distant lands when paradise is at your paws?
Text.LocalizedString: This desert, with its harsh beauty and rugged charm, is home. Why seek distant lands when paradise is at your paws?

Text.SourceString: Ah, it's raining! Today's a good day.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, it's raining! Today's a good day.

Text.SourceString: Look at this rain! Amazing!//This rain, it's a blessing upon the desert.
Text.LocalizedString: Look at this rain! Amazing!//This rain, it's a blessing upon the desert.

Text.SourceString: Ah, it's raining! Today's a good day.//Thank you, skies, for this rain.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, it's raining! Today's a good day.//Thank you, skies, for this rain.

Text.SourceString: I feel a deep sense of gratitude with this rain. It's a rare gift.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel a deep sense of gratitude with this rain. It's a rare gift.
